evidence.text: For the reasons stated above, the Court DENIES the parties’ motions for approval of settlement (Dkt. Nos. 234 and 235). Accordingly, though the Panel will conduct a status conference on Tuesday April 26, 2022 at 1:00 p.m., it will not hear arguments regarding the authority of the House Defendants and Plaintiff to settle their claims at that time. The trial, previously noticed to commence on May 16, 2022, will proceed as scheduled. AND IT IS SO ORDERED.
